data.description: Wanted: Someone to love. Split Foyer home on a nice, fenced lot is looking for a new owner to give it some more updates. This home has some hardwood floors on the main level, newer cabinets in a large kitchen with rear deck access.  A fourth bedroom is located on the lower level adjacent to the laundry area. There are two full baths, one on each level. A wood stove on the lower level makes the space warm and cozy. This home sweet home is an easy commute to shopping and major traffic routes, yet it is nestled in a well-established neighborhood. American Home Sheild warranty offered. Don't miss this one!
